{"tid":1968540,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"【現眼報】46歲男警長仍危殆 醫管局暫未掌握惡化因由","createTime":"2020-04-11T17:46:23.000Z","updateTime":"2020-04-12T11:51:56.000Z","uid":239336,"like":75,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":49,"replies":[{"pid":"0695a563c8fac43e507025dc0ea5ceece916d87d","tid":1968540,"uid":239336,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-11T17:46:23.000Z","msg":"昨日多個傳媒追問46歲警長的中招情況但不獲回應，醫院管理局總行政經理何婉霞今日（11日）解釋，昨日沒有數據所以未能回答，翻查資料後得知該警長並非長期病患者，但他的呼吸情況不理想，需要用呼吸機及處方抗病毒藥物。她指明白大家想知病人惡化背後的原因，目前只講到惡化現象，惡化原因要臨床診斷才掌握。<br />\n<br />\n昨日有15人危殆，當中6位是50歲以下，另有5位是與854號病人相似，都是40幾歲病人；部份人非長期病患。何婉霞指由於今次肺炎始終是新病，外國見到一些年輕患者情況都會較差，需要時間研究病情，現在要專心醫好每個病人，「邊啲病人會惡化，都要外國數據先了解到。」<br />\n<br />\n衞生防護中心傳染病處主任張竹君補充指，其他逾百名密切接觸的警員暫無初步確診，推測洗手間是傳播途徑。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/20200411/NBWFEQCD3YKPURBYHRARHGIQPY/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200411%2FNBWFEQCD3YKPURBYHRARHGIQPY%2F&d=pQk%2FYDfxyk1It%2BdH9Wj1W5mCY7kjLy3g2NNjbjbrEl8%3D&h=ef41fc2c\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200411%2FNBWFEQCD3YKPURBYHRARHGIQPY%2F&h=ad25352e\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/20200411/NBWFEQCD3YKPURBYHRARHGIQPY/</a>"},{"pid":"89c4df8b457d75c7cc6b67c5f320b86cdc173281","tid":1968540,"uid":10070,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-11T17:47:10.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/clap.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/clap.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/clap.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/clap.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7b95fbe8af369c90650ac22bd34fdcfa5479cf37","tid":1968540,"uid":239336,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-11T17:48:15.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b228f2f95bf7d817717a2fec9387f67d44f705a4","tid":1968540,"uid":